reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect and functional
reviews.reviewText: I previously had a suction cup one inside the sink. It would take up room and get food in it. This helped free up space in my sink and has a clean and functional look. I have one in my kitchen and one in my kids bathroom for his orthodontic tools and cup, the side spot is perfect for his toothpaste. It’s just the right size.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for sink counter organization
reviews.reviewText: Bought this to keep all the sink plugs, sponges and dish scrubber off my sink area and more organized. So far this caddy has been working perfectly for my needs. It's the perfect size for the items and even has a tray that fits underneath to catch excess water that's easy to slide out to clean. It's big enough to hold all the items in the description picture but small enough not to be too bulky. Happy with this purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect sink caddy
reviews.reviewText: We are very pleased with this caddy. I really like that it sits on the counter and there is a small tray to catch any water. The tray is removable so it can be easily emptied into the sink. It is the perfect item to add to your kitchen organization project. I am going to purchase one for my in-laws.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: In the photos, I have my dish soap and baby bottle soap, bottle brush, and sponge all fit in this. Some reviews made me doubt whether I’d be able to fit the soaps in, but as you can see from the picture there’s plenty of room. Overall, it makes my counter look really tidy and clean. There’s a plastic piece underneath that collects water. It’s a little inconvenient that it doesn’t have a drain spout, but not a deal breaker. There’s also four black rubber pieces on the bottom so the caddy doesn’t slide around easily. 9/10 recommend.
